类 Word

java.lang.Object
q2.Word
所有已实现的接口:
Comparable<Word>
public class Word extends Object implements Comparable<Word>
A class that includes the word and its frequency. Provides methods to get the word, get and increment its frequency, and compare objects based on frequency.
